        dc:description           "FIGURE 4. Tyrannosaurid fossils collected from the Naashoibito Member of the Kirtland Formation and the MCRae Formation. A-F, AMNH 5882, right pedal phalanx (D IV,?PH H) in A, medial, B, proximal, C, lateral, D, distal, E, dorsal, and F, ventral views. G-H, NMMNH P-3698, right palatine in G, lateral, and H, medial views. I, NNIMNH P-13000, dentary or maxillary tooth crown in lingual view. I-K, left dentary in I, lateral and, K, medial views." ;
